{"tid":2458184,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"官方正服：魔力寶永恆初心 Telegram group","createTime":"2021-03-23T08:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T03:43:18.000Z","uid":59090,"like":7,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"daa0c73dd2f5c668d769e92aa5efcdcc66a1d07a","tid":2458184,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7WHzYTW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7WHzYTW.jpg&h=f0e2e7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為黎緊最快兩日後(3月25至4月頭)公測,想搵多D 香港人一齊夾住黎玩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下多個Telegram Group會唔會令大家交流緊密少少( Me比較少用其他App)<br />\n<br />\n如果只可以三帳既話,我生產系應該會淨係做廚師+2獵,到時大家多多捧場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個Telegram Group主要係為以下用途:<br />\n<br />\n玩家交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩家交易(有封印巴打既話，預訂靚掉黑鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n組隊練功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n組隊解任打王<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n資源整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">入谷連結： <a href=\"http://t.me/crossgate00\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcrossgate00&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97btp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=b01c2fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/crossgate00</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家有時間幫我推下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4072521ccfefafb3fd89bc6c3de6e6f6c52b45e","tid":2458184,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb410ff17f970ed8638b9892980816b9dd596a33","tid":2458184,"uid":59090,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"rep